    <item>
      <title>由于美国家电需求仍然停滞不前，惠而浦将裁员 1,000 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/whirlpool-whr-layoffs-amount-to-1-000-salaried-office-jobs-to-help-cut-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国房屋销售放缓限制了需求，Maytag 和 Amana 家电品牌的所有者惠而浦公司 (Whirlpool Corp.) 正在全球范围内削减约 1,000 个带薪职位，以降低成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/whirlpool-whr-layoffs-amount-to-1-000-salaried-office-jobs-to-help-cut-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 20:10:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗集团考虑为 Berry 和 Glatfelter 提供 20 亿美元债务方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/citi-eyes-2-billion-debt-package-for-berry-glatfelter-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团和富国银行据知情人士透露，公司正在准备一项 20 亿美元的债务计划，以支持 Berry Global Group Inc. 将其大部分健康、卫生和特色业务分拆给 Glatfelter Corp.。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/citi-eyes-2-billion-debt-package-for-berry-glatfelter-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 20:03:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
